  "texts": [
    "The remainder of this paper is organized as follows.",
    "We provide a succinct background on the analysis of maps in section 2 to keep the paper self-contained with respect to the structural characteristics that are used in our evaluation.",
    "Then, we present our approach in section 3 with an emphasis on filters, and we evaluate it in section 4 on two domains and four documents.",
    "Finally, we discuss these results in section 5 with respect to the feasibility of using GPT-3.5 models to extract causal maps from text.",
    "To support transparency and replicability efforts, our scripts are permanently available at https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8045304."
  ],
